Class Hero

  • java.lang.Object
    • Person
      • Hero
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Guardian, Knight, mentalMonk, pathFinder, Trickster, watchDog

    public class Hero
extends Person
    Date: April 29th 2018 Hero class is parent class to all types of Heroes. The class provides Object Hero attributes such as Health, Skill, Dice, Armour and Maximum Health. Includes getter and setter methods for Attributes.
    Author:
    Sachin Sakthivel and Sasiru Goonatillake

      • checkdeath

        public void checkdeath​()
        This method checks whether the Hero has more than 1 health and if not set Boolean variable Living to false in parent class Person. If Hero is dead a popUp window is displayed to the user notifying the user of the Hero's death.
